Sweden's Henrik Stenson and Australian Jason Day jointly hold the major record at 20 under.
The women's record of 19 under is shared by four players.
"The game plan for tomorrow [Sunday] is just to keep doing the same thing," said Chun, who is in her first year on the LPGA Tour.
"I'm not going to think about winning. I just want to keep enjoying what I am doing."
